    "There are many directions for improvement.",
    "We outline some of them, dividing them up from the perspective of data, modeling, and learning.",
    "From a data perspective, a direct solution could be to apply our strategies of designing adversarial probes to augment the training data.",
    "Our simple attempt (see Appendix.5) shows that this can effectively improve the model performance on the probe data and the original test data.",
    "Aside from training data, new video testing benchmarks are emerging (Li et al., 2024a; Fu et al., 2024; Liu et al., 2024b; Li et al., 2024b)."
